---
import ZhLayout from '../../../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout
  title="工业清洁机 | DGSDK 史帝克"
  description="史帝克专业工业清洁机：偏光片清洁机、FPC清洁机、PCB清洁机、SMT清洁机、光学薄膜清洁机、LCM清洁机等，适用于精密制造行业。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/products/cleaning-machine"
>
  <section
    class="products-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/cleaning-machine/cnc.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;"
  >
    <div class="container products-hero-inner">
      <span class="products-hero-kicker">史帝克产品系列</span>
      <h1>工业清洁机</h1>
      <p>
        专业工业清洁解决方案，适用于PCB、FPC、偏光片、背光板、光学薄膜、SMT、LCM及其他精密制造应用。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="products-overview-section">
    <div class="container products-overview-layout">
      <aside class="products-sidebar">
        <div class="products-sidebar-box">
          <h3>产品分类</h3>
          <a href="/zh/products">所有产品</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator">静电消除系统</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine" class="active-category">工业清洁机</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts">精密加工零件</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/automation">自动化设备</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="products-main">
        <section class="apple-product-section">
          <div class="apple-card-grid">
            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner.jpg" alt="偏光片精密清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>偏光片精密清洁机</h3>
              <p>专为敏感偏光片表面的清洁稳定处理而设计。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/fpc-4-axis-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/fpc-4-axis-cleaner.jpg" alt="FPC四轴高精度清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>FPC四轴高精度清洁机</h3>
              <p>适用于柔性印刷电路应用的高精度清洁系统。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/fpc-8-axis-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/fpc-8-axis-cleaner.jpg" alt="FPC八轴高端清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>FPC八轴高端清洁机</h3>
              <p>满足高要求生产工作流的先进多轴清洁平台。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/optical-film-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/optical.jpg" alt="大尺寸光学薄膜清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>大尺寸光学薄膜清洁机</h3>
              <p>适用于大幅面光学薄膜应用的工业表面清洁设备。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/lcm-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/lcm-cleaner.jpg" alt="LCM模组工业清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>LCM模组工业清洁机</h3>
              <p>适用于模组处理和显示屏组装生产线的工业清洁系统。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/pcb-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/pcb-cleaner.jpg" alt="PCB表面清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>PCB表面清洁机</h3>
              <p>PCB制造和检验阶段的稳定表面清洁设备。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/pcb-vertical-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/stick-pcb-vertical-cleaning-machine.jpg" alt="PCB垂直清洁系统" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>PCB垂直清洁系统</h3>
              <p>垂直清洁设计，高效支持PCB工艺流程。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/roll-chip-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/roll-chip-cleaner.jpg" alt="滚轮通用清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>滚轮通用清洁机</h3>
              <p>适用于滚轮和精密物料处理的通用清洁解决方案。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/smt-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/smt-cleaner.jpg" alt="SMT在线清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>SMT在线清洁机</h3>
              <p>SMT工艺和精密装配线的在线清洁支持设备。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/backlight-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/backlight-cleaner.jpg" alt="背光板清洁机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>背光板清洁机</h3>
              <p>适用于背光板生产环境的精密清洁设备。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/ccl-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/ccl-cleaner.jpg" alt="史帝克CCL清洁机 ST DT1340" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>史帝克CCL清洁机 ST DT1340</h3>
              <p>为CCL相关工业制造线提供稳定清洁支持。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/inspection-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/inspection-cleaner.jpg" alt="检验台清洁机（STXT系列）" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
              <h3>检验台清洁机（STXT系列）</h3>
              <p>为精密生产工作流提供集成检验和清洁支持。</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ZhLayout>
